// V0.20.42: QUEST DIALOGUE & NARRATIVE PASS - Roadmap Item 1 (Dark Woods Quest Dialogue Overhaul), COMPLETE. All 26 Dark Woods quests audited against the roadmap's 8 dialogue states with a standalone harness, then the REAL render paths were read to separate genuine gaps from false positives - the session's recurring lesson turned on the audit itself. THREE real fixes shipped, each root-caused in its owning module. (1) FAILURE DIALOGUE FOR DEFENSE EVENTS (state 5): a defend hold that breaks used to speak only a fixed system-narrator line, the same for every quest - the ESCORT path was the only one honouring an authored failureText. A new quest-system logDefendFailure() now routes every defend failure (overrun / left-gate / hold-timeout) through the quest's own in-character line first, then the mechanical reset note (a defend is retryable, unlike the permanent escort loss); quests with no failureText keep their exact old behaviour. Authored failureText for the 3 defends that lacked it: quest_guides_warning, quest_what_the_gap_lets_in, quest_the_long_root. (2) IN-CHARACTER IN-PROGRESS (state 3, 'must remain in character rather than repeating raw objective text'): quest_the_long_root literally SPOKE '(300s)' and '6 waves' and three night quests shouted 'NIGHT ONLY' - dev/UI notation in an NPC's mouth that the validator's word-list missed. 11 flat objective-restatements rewritten into each NPC's voice; the mechanical detail already lives in the task labels and the live defend HUD, so nothing is lost. (3) POST-COMPLETION (state 8) for quest_ruriks_bargain, whose giver Rurik lives on the ally path and was replaying his turn-in line. HARDENED THE VALIDATOR (Item 22 discipline): validateQuestDialogue now also flags parenthetical seconds-notation like '(300s)', proven NON-VACUOUS (catches the old line, passes clean prose and ordinary numbers). FALSE POSITIVES DOCUMENTED, NOT PADDED: the 6 'missing lockedText' are prereq-only quests that never reach the lockedText path (it is paired with requiredConditions by design); the 5 'missing beforeOfferText' and 10 'missing postCompletionText' are giver-less breadcrumbs, branch/auto-offer quests, and repeatable dailies that re-offer - none has a speaker or a render path for those states. Suite PASS, 0 validator violations, 0 console errors. See docs/V0.20.42_QUEST_DIALOGUE_PASS.md.
